title: Bachman Cummings Songbook (2006, SonyBMG) [flac]
description:
Randy Bachman-Burton Cummings - Bachman Cummings Songbook -2006
 <a href="

A greatest hits compilation from Canada's most famous rock duo.
Contains nine of the very best from The Guess Who, five from
Bachman-Turner Overdrive, and five solo Burton Cummings.
A very tasty treat of solid classic rock hits.
